{"tid":2224150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃色經濟圈《佔領立法會》和《幻愛》榮獲台灣金馬獎重要獎項提名","createTime":"2020-09-30T10:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T14:42:32.000Z","uid":134071,"like":50,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ef067ec816475fe474f4b58282abac093181ddec","tid":2224150,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈電影《佔領立法會》和《幻愛》榮獲台灣金馬獎既重要獎項提名.<br />\n<br />\n《佔領立法會》榮獲最佳紀錄片的提名.&nbsp;(導演掛名為「香港紀錄片工作者」)<br />\n《幻愛》榮獲最佳改篇劇本 (曾俊榮, 周冠威), 最佳新演員(劉俊謙), 最佳音效(杜篤之、吳書瑤)的提名.<br />\n<br />\n今次再證明,&nbsp;<strong>黃色經濟圈唔只有良心,&nbsp;仲有質素.</strong>&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第57屆金馬獎入圍名單&nbsp;(好快會有full&nbsp;list)<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3308180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3308180&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=d1ce476f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3308180&h=c939b3e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3308180</a>"},{"pid":"2c8c1ed1e353bc85d4dc9455444d315eb20d3108","tid":2224150,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:12:16.000Z","msg":"另一方面,&nbsp;也有多套香港電影獲重要獎項提名<br />\n<br />\n《墮胎師》 (提名包括最佳導演, etc...)<br />\n《手捲煙》 (提名包括最佳劇情長片,etc...)<br />\n《狂舞派3》.&nbsp; (提名包括最佳改篇劇本, 最佳動作設計, etc...)"},{"pid":"80896e646bcf594d69271584d7c7be33fbb0e879","tid":2224150,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持本土電影"},{"pid":"7032afa1b7603c2f97f82c060d0090cd1ade0696","tid":2224150,"uid":232157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"